1007
01:09:50,787 --> 01:09:54,518
Neka tvoj narod sazna pakao
koji se pravi u njihovo ime.

1008
01:09:57,157 --> 01:09:58,368
Uradi to!

1009
01:10:07,187 --> 01:10:09,172
Lucy, uzmi pištolj!

1010
01:10:14,110 --> 01:10:15,987
Dosta!

1011
01:10:16,946 --> 01:10:19,039
