1012
01:10:19,381 --> 01:10:23,509
Uradi to još jednom i
razneću ti mozak po zidu.

1013
01:10:23,519 --> 01:10:24,520
Sedi!

1014
01:10:26,253 --> 01:10:27,709
Slomilo se.

1015
01:10:28,453 --> 01:10:31,652
